onlineBanking web application built with ASP.NET Core MVC.


### ✅ Clean Architecture
    * Domain (Entities only)
    * Application (Interfaces + Rules)
    * Infrastructure (DB, PDF, Security)
    * Web (MVC + UI)


✅ Customer Registration
   Name, Email, City, Password দিয়ে register → ৫ ডিজিট Auto-generated 5-digit Account Number
   * Email unique (duplicate হলে register হবে না)
   * Password BCrypt hash হয়ে DB-তে store হয়

✅ Admin Functionalities:
    * All customers list view
    * Make / Remove Admin
    * Lock customer account (manual)
    * Unlock customer account
    * Reset customer password
    * View full Audit Logs

✅ Security Features:
   * Password hashing (BCrypt)
   * CSRF protection (Auto Anti-Forgery)
   * Brute-force protection (lockout)
   * Cookie hardening
   * Secure headers:
     * X-Frame-Options
     * X-Content-Type-Options
     * CSP
   * HTTPS ready (IIS friendly)

✅ Audit Logs (Real Banking Feature)
   -Every sensitive action record হয়
   -system কে কখন কী করেছে দেখতে পারা


✅ Withdraw Money
   * Balance sufficient না হলে withdraw হবে না
   * Minimum Balance Rule enforced
   * Transaction record হয়
   * Audit log হয়

 ✅ Deposit Money
   * Positive amount check
   * Balance বাড়ে
   * Transaction table-এ record হয়
   * Audit log তৈরি হয়

✅ Transfer Money
   * এক account থেকে অন্য account-এ transfer
   * Same account-এ transfer block
   * Receiver account exist না করলে fail
   * Daily Transfer Limit enforced
   * Minimum balance after transfer enforce
   * Sender → TransferOut
   * Receiver → TransferIn
   * Double transaction entry (ledger style)
   * Audit log হয় (actor + target)


✅ PDF Mini Statement
   * Downloadable PDF
   * Last 10 transactions
   * Customer name, account number
   * Current balance
   * Asia/Dhaka time conversion
   * Currency symbol configurable (৳ / € / $)

